					"type": 23,
					"value": "Short dialog between a child and his mom, who have come in the Sorcerous Sundries shop, presumably to buy something. The kid is looking at the enourmous lava elemental near it.\r\n\"Mumbus\" is the kid's name for his mom, pronounced how it looks (mum-bus)"
